<div id="review_2195376531" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/2195376531" />
    <a title="Addie H" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/16858463-addie-h"><img alt="Addie H" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1511793475p2/16858463.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/2195376531?book_show_action=true">Sep 05, 2019</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Addie H" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Addie H" href="/user/show/16858463-addie-h">Addie H</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="really liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">really liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Kindle Edition " href="/book/show/36512098-snow-flower-and-the-secret-fan">review of another edition</a>


        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/16858463-addie-h?shelf=b-comp-hist-fic">b-comp-hist-fic</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2195376531" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer2776896823650109866"><i>I have a whole life to tell; I have nothing left to lose and few to offend.</i><br/><br/>Three quarters of this book was fascinating. An enthralling glimpse of a way of life in China that was beyond harsh. I was utterly enthralled to read about the friendship between Snow Flower and Lily. <br/><br/>The last quarter takes a surprisingly dark twist, and it threw me a bit. There are some rather dramatic events that felt a bit out of place, and ultimately I didn&apos;t quite understand Lily&apos;s extreme behaviour.<br/><br/>That said, the en</span>
  <span id="freeText2776896823650109866" style="display:none"><i>I have a whole life to tell; I have nothing left to lose and few to offend.</i><br /><br />Three quarters of this book was fascinating. An enthralling glimpse of a way of life in China that was beyond harsh. I was utterly enthralled to read about the friendship between Snow Flower and Lily. <br /><br />The last quarter takes a surprisingly dark twist, and it threw me a bit. There are some rather dramatic events that felt a bit out of place, and ultimately I didn't quite understand Lily's extreme behaviour.<br /><br />That said, the ending brought it somewhat nicely back together. <br /><br />The writing is very beautiful, and I would definitely recommend reading this unique, fictional historical novel.</span>
