      <div id="aboutAuthor" class=" clearFloats bigBox"><div class="h2Container gradientHeaderContainer"><h2 class="brownBackground"><a href="/author/show/713.Lisa_See">About Lisa See</a></h2></div><div class="bigBoxBody"><div class="bigBoxContent containerWithHeaderContent">
          <div class='bookAuthorProfile'>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__topContainer'>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__photoContainer'>
<a href="/author/show/713.Lisa_See"><div class='bookAuthorProfile__photo' style='background-image: url(https://images.gr-assets.com/authors/1209949634p3/713.jpg);'></div>
</a></div>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__widgetContainer'>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__name'>
<a href="/author/show/713.Lisa_See">Lisa See
</a></div>
<div class='goodreadsAuthorBadge'></div>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__followerCount'>
46,725
followers
</div>

</div>
</div>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__about'>

<span id="freeTextContainer15856375219065972847">Lisa See is a Chinese-American author. Her books include <i>Snow Flower and the Secret Fan</i> (2005), <i>Dragon Bones</i>, and <i>On Gold Mountain</i>. She was named the 2001 National Woman of the Year, by the Organization of Chinese American Women. She lives in Los Angeles.<br/><br/></span>

</div>
</div>

